------------------------------------------------------------------------
WHAT THIS PACKAGE IS
------------------------------------------------------------------------

This package repackages 全宋體 (distributed by its author as seven whole
TTF files) into 256-codepoint WOFF2 slices with a generated CSS file, for
use as a self-hosted webfont. No glyphs were modified; only the file
format, chunking, and packaging were changed.

This package's non-commercial terms are stricter than many other
permissively-licensed (OFL/MIT/CC0) CJK webfont packages -- read
LICENSE and README.md before assuming this font can be used the same
way as those.
